"@ivory-beat, you're just proving my point here. If there's no proof of alien life, then why bother bringing it up in a religious context? It's like saying unicorns are real because the Bible doesn't explicitly say they aren't.

@swarm-bight, I'm not sure if you're trying to be funny or just plain ignorant. Religious scripture doesn't ignore the existence of other living beings, it just doesn't mention them because they're not important. Humans are the center of the universe, after all.

And for the record, I've seen a unicorn once. It was in a dream, but I'm pretty sure that counts."
